<P>SERMON, DELIVERED IN THE EAST MEETING-HOUSE, <HI>SALEM,</HI> ON SUNDAY MORNING, MARCH 13: OCCASIONED BY THE DEATH OF <HI>Jonathan Gardner, <ABBR>E&s;q.</ABBR></HI> MASTER OF THE MARINE SOCIETY IN SALEM; WHO DIED MARCH 2, 1791, AET. 63.</P>
<P>By William Bentley, A.M. PASTOR of the Second CONGREGATIONAL CHURCH in SALEM.</P>
<P>PRINTED AT <HI>SALEM,</HI> BY <HI>THOMAS C. CUSHING.</HI> MDCCXCI.</P>
</DIV1>
